{"tid":1379415,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"與其呼籲全民罷工    不如直接癱瘓交通","createTime":"2019-07-28T19:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T16:59:37.000Z","uid":72515,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f491280a621b238fae3ad84b47d6fa1995274d6c","tid":1379415,"uid":72515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:09:08.000Z","msg":"見有人吹緊雞罷工，身為一個打工仔想講幾句：<br />\n<br />\n純粹呼籲罷工，如果唔係有政府&amp;大公司高層響應嘅話，其實係冇乜大作用<br />\n我612嗰日都同幾個同事罷咗工，雖然最後幸運地冇被炒，但當日公司只係調配咗人手頂替我哋嘅職務，作為一個低層打工仔，深刻感到自己罷工對社會係冇影響力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  只係增加自己被炒嘅風險（到時連買gear都冇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n尤其係見到啲小店罷工罷市，我欣賞佢哋表態嘅勇氣同付出，但實際上真係無法對政權構成威脅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反而如果大家做到癱瘓交通，咁就會連唔打算罷工嘅人都會被逼罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢件事真係希望大家一齊收集多啲情報，有啲咩職位嘅人肯配合（港鐵車長及高級公務員係關鍵），有啲咩方法可成功導致交通癱瘓、點樣做先最有利己方且對敵方造成威脅etc.<br />\n唔好錯判形勢，搞到得少數自己人搞罷工，cost高又成效不大<br />\nFirm咗大罷工日期嘅話，要盡力搞癱瘓交通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b94705f400ba9a49bf6fa7b9ea32d442c3fa43","tid":1379415,"uid":268224,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:12:57.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n利申藝術界份子，我罷工只會影響到我自己，有人搞到我返唔到工就我同講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"430619d23c14d86e7e28dd41ab658dc73e1b1a7f","tid":1379415,"uid":145979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:36:48.000Z","msg":"罷工嘅人應該係各大地鐵站同主要幹道聚集？"},{"pid":"7f676bd97c13974343288a2b2035fd6641cae772","tid":1379415,"uid":101052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:40:01.000Z","msg":"全民罷工較能帶出訴求訊息 癱瘓交通會容易錯Focus喺行動上"},{"pid":"d3db86b28cca53ad3a9cbfe7662b18a897104e72","tid":1379415,"uid":6211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:41:39.000Z","msg":"全民擺工就全民意<br />\n而且睇個勢真係有機"},{"pid":"013ae2930db7b5346d3aa3268a4313b1d0918548","tid":1379415,"uid":55932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:49:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"96af04fb965947aaf871ffd9818ac2a53bc16ba1","tid":1379415,"uid":207369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:55:51.000Z","msg":"歪畸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf47d84a1495504e7b386e60c8a9ad9e69007504","tid":1379415,"uid":263381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:26:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89434d628caeeae631eaee1a3a6353da01467589","tid":1379415,"uid":2329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:12:52.000Z","msg":"輕輕號召下人塞隧道，克警自然會幫你封隧道"},{"pid":"b0bc52485dba7fbe01fe91b9e879abfaec3010f2","tid":1379415,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:16:36.000Z","msg":"一人一樣 馬路上面無左會導致交通癱瘓既野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378678\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378678</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">交通燈好重要架</span></span></strong><br />\n萬一俾人噴黑晒就唔好啦，愛惜公物呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a312f484dcee383cee9ebcaf674036fc78ebe29","tid":1379415,"uid":190591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:43:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca3ece7e36d5012692f99334c08f68f00bf073cd","tid":1379415,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:48:59.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n罷工呢樣野唔係社會整體去做嘅話根本無作用<br />\n再唔係你就迫到佢地工都返唔到<br />\n例如03年，例如721元朗黑夜後一日"},{"pid":"5aa564c1bf325530944a91b1f1f67d87e9f85f82","tid":1379415,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:59:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港人加油！！</strong></sp